version_description: This tab represents the full studio album of Crowded House's Woodface. There are multiple capo changes but all standard tuning.
Easy to play on guitar the key range suits me, it may suit someone else aswell.
Tidied up for 2018 with appropriate verse and chord sections.
Other Akkords and other all text lines, better for learning.
This version includes the chords for the solo and the ending.
